new equipment, new devices,
and his famous line was--

01:22:17.730 --> 01:22:20.690
after they'd been working for
months and months on a new piece

01:22:20.690 --> 01:22:24.060
of machinery, he'd say,
Alright boys, let's start her

01:22:24.060 --> 01:22:27.680
and see why she doesn't work.

01:22:27.680 --> 01:22:33.310
That's what we're about, it's
call the Empirical Method.

01:22:33.310 --> 01:22:34.610
You do-- you try something,

01:22:34.610 --> 01:22:36.640
and if it doesn't work you
study why it doesn't work,

01:22:36.640 --> 01:22:40.440
and then you fix it, and then
maybe eventually it will work.

01:22:40.440 --> 01:22:43.240
It's been true all along.

01:22:43.240 --> 01:22:47.280
And we are constantly making
progress which we don't recognize

01:22:47.280 --> 01:22:49.730
as progress because we're in the
thick of it, we're in the midst

01:22:49.730 --> 01:22:53.330
of it, as everybody always was.

01:22:53.330 --> 01:22:57.650
When you think for example,
what's happened in our country,

01:22:57.650 --> 01:23:02.490
in our lifetime, in medicine,
it's utterly phenomenal.

01:23:02.490 --> 01:23:05.710
I think that future historians
may very well, while looking back

01:23:05.710 --> 01:23:11.170
on our time, say, well that's
what real history was then,

01:23:11.170 --> 01:23:13.690
that was history being made.

01:23:13.690 --> 01:23:17.990
And it comes from ideas,
it comes from education,

01:23:17.990 --> 01:23:22.420
it comes from imagination,
and genius, yes.

01:23:22.420 --> 01:23:27.510
It does happen, because some people
really have that touch of genius,

01:23:27.510 --> 01:23:30.290
and they should be part of History.

01:23:30.290 --> 01:23:33.730
Those doctors who's names we don't
figure at all, we should know

01:23:33.730 --> 01:23:38.000
who they were, and what
they did, just as is true

01:23:38.000 --> 01:23:41.080
about our painters and our writers.

01:23:41.080 --> 01:23:44.900
I thank my lucky stars that
I quit my job in New York,

01:23:44.900 --> 01:23:47.660
and came to this city when I did.

01:23:47.660 --> 01:23:52.050
It not only changed my
outlook, it changed my life,

01:23:52.050 --> 01:23:57.850
but it's given me ambitions
to expand the experience

01:23:57.850 --> 01:24:01.220
of being alive, through
the experience of history,

01:24:01.220 --> 01:24:04.330 position:56%
